### Noticeboard API — request examples
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Variables (fill after login)
@accessToken =
@refreshToken =
@announcementId = 1

### -------------------------------------------------------------------------
### AUTH
### -------------------------------------------------------------------------

### Register a new user
# @name register
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "ivan_petrenko",
  "name": "Ivan",
  "password": "qwerty123"
}

### Login (demo user: ivan_petrenko / qwerty123)
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "ivan_petrenko",
  "password": "qwerty123"
}

### Current user (copy accessToken from login/register above)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Refresh tokens using the refreshToken cookie
# (refresh token is stored in HttpOnly cookie "refreshToken")
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh
Cookie: refreshToken={{refreshToken}}

### Logout — revokes refresh token and clears cookie
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Cookie: refreshToken={{refreshToken}}

### -------------------------------------------------------------------------
### Rate limit test — run this >10 times within 15 min to get 429
### -------------------------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "username": "ivan_petrenko", "password": "wrong" }

### -------------------------------------------------------------------------
### ANNOUNCEMENTS
### -------------------------------------------------------------------------

### List — default pagination (page=1, limit=5)
GET {{baseUrl}}/announcements

### List — search in title
GET {{baseUrl}}/announcements?search=iPhone

### List — filter by category
GET {{baseUrl}}/announcements?category=sale

### List — sort by price asc
GET {{baseUrl}}/announcements?sortBy=price&order=asc

### List — combined: page 2, limit 10, sale, newest first
GET {{baseUrl}}/announcements?page=2&limit=10&category=sale&sortBy=createdAt&order=desc

### List — invalid query (expect 400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/announcements?sortBy=invalidField

### Get one announcement
GET {{baseUrl}}/announcements/{{announcementId}}

### Get non-existent (expect 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/announcements/999999

### Create — JSON, no image (requires access token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/announcements
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Продам велосипед",
  "description": "Трек у відмінному стані, майже новий.",
  "price": 8500,
  "category": "sale",
  "contactInfo": "seller@example.com"
}

### Create — multipart/form-data with image
POST {{baseUrl}}/announcements
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----NB

------NB
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

Продам камеру
------NB
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

Дзеркальна камера, ідеальний стан, в комплекті об'єктив.
------NB
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="price"

12000
------NB
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="category"

sale
------NB
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="contactInfo"

seller@example.com
------NB
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="photo.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./public/photo.jpg
------NB--

### Validation error — title too short (expect 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/announcements
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "abc",
  "description": "too short desc",
  "price": 10,
  "category": "sale",
  "contactInfo": "x@y.z"
}

### Protected route without token (expect 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/announcements
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "No token here",
  "description": "This should be rejected with 401.",
  "price": 100,
  "category": "sale",
  "contactInfo": "nobody@example.com"
}

### Partial update — JSON (owner only)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/announcements/{{announcementId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "price": 7999 }

### Partial update with new image — multipart
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/announcements/{{announcementId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----NB

------NB
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="new.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./public/photo.jpg
------NB--

### Delete (owner only) — expect 204
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/announcements/{{announcementId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
